# Failure Handling in Durable Functions

## Retry Policies

Automatically retry failed activities.

## Compensation Transactions

Undo completed operations when a later step fails.

Example:

* Payment completed
* Shipment failed
* Refund payment

## Error Handling

Use try-catch in orchestrator functions.

## Dead Letter Queue

Can be implemented using Service Bus for failed processing.

